---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Prose from '../../components/Prose.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
    <Prose>
        <h1>About <span class="text-gradient">me</span></h1>
        
        <p>
            Hi! My name is <strong>Valentin</strong>. 
            Welcome to my corner of the web.
        </p>

        <p>
            I created this blog to document my learning journey and share my experiences.
            Launching <strong>vbesse.com</strong> is a way for me to master modern web technologies
            like Astro and understand how continuous deployment works.
        </p>

        <h3>What I love</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Discovering new frameworks (like Astro!).</li>
            <li>Web optimization and performance.</li>
            <li>Minimalist design.</li>
        </ul>

        <blockquote>
            "Learning by doing is the best way to progress."
        </blockquote>
    </Prose>
</Layout>